41:31.589 --> 41:37.628 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And, again, they were caught
between these
two different worlds, the pro
Assad forces

41:37.662 --> 41:43.468 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
and the anti-Assad forces,
