41:48.106 --> 41:54.645 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Plus -- plus, I should mention,
Hari, that
both Hasan and the son, the
18-year-old son

41:54.679 --> 41:59.851 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
of Suhila and Ramy, were being
drafted to
