42:06.124 --> 42:10.428 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: So, Katie, how
did these
families get to Lesbos to be
picked by the

42:10.461 --> 42:11.729 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
pope?

42:11.763 --> 42:14.132 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
KATIE COURIC: Well, Hari, first,
they had
to make it to Turkey.

42:14.165 --> 42:19.203 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And Hasan and Nour stayed in
