exclusive.

49:21.792 --> 49:26.797 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
I have been arrested six
different times,
all the while in a delusional,
paranoid state

49:26.831 --> 49:32.069 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
of mind caused by my illness.
