making a
certain decision, so I change
the station

49:47.484 --> 49:55.759 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
just to spite them. I throw
three fingers
up at a public security camera
and tell President

49:55.793 --> 49:58.929 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
