49:58.963 --> 50:03.167 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
No, the rules of society don't
apply to me,
not when I'm having one of my
episodes.

50:03.200 --> 50:05.769 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
I just raise my hand like this.

50:05.803 --> 50:10.875 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
My episodes, which are rare, can
happen at
any time and take many forms,
from creating

50:10.908 --> 50:16.280 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
a piece of art, to aggressively
accusing UPS
employees of being government
workers smuggling

50:16.313 --> 50:18.682 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
weapons through their delivery
routes.

50:18.716 --> 50:22.820 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I'm able to show you these
pictures because
my wife has documented these
episodes, so

50:22.853 --> 50:26.457 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
that we can learn more about
myself and ultimately
help others learn.

50:26.490 --> 50:31.929 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WOMAN: My gosh, this is a mess.
You created
a studio up here, baby. You look
like a true

50:31.962 --> 50:32.796 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
artist.

50:32.830 --> 50:34.698 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
PATON BLOUGH: You see, I'm not
alone.

50:34.732 --> 50:39.436 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
More than half of all prison and
jail inmates
have a mental health issue. You
can imagine

50:39.470 --> 50:43.807 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
the kind of reaction someone
like me might
have when delusions trigger an
incident in

50:43.841 --> 50:48.846 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
which a police officer wants to
engage with
me or, worse, arrest me.

50:48.879 --> 50:54.118 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Three of my six arrests went
relatively well,
with police getting me into
custody safely.

50:54.151 --> 50:58.289 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The other three were extremely
violent, because,
in my head, I was fighting for
my life.

50:58.322 --> 51:02.359 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I was Tased in the back of the
police car
in our hospital parking lot with
leg irons

51:02.393 --> 51:07.631 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
