51:09.466 --> 51:13.938 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Thankfully, around six years
ago, my recovery
killed into high gear. I was
asked to share

51:13.971 --> 51:20.277 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
